text: Guillaume Tell (8 July 1902 - 6 October 1998) was a French long-distance runner. He competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1998 deaths Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:French male long-distance runners Category:French male marathon runners Category:Olympic athletes of France
